TEXT_DATA.TEXT: This is a consumer specification for Lipton Orange Passionfruit Jasmine Superfruit Green Tea - 20ct.
GREEN TEA, ORANGE PEEL, JASMINE TEA, NATURAL FLAVOR, SOY LECITHIN.

Regular and Decaf (Cup of Hot Green Tea) Brew in boiling water 1 to 1-1/2 minutes or to desired strength; remove tea bag; sweeten to taste.
Regular and Decaf (Quart of Iced Green Tea) Brew 4 tea bags in two cups of boiling water in heat-proof pitcher. Brew 1 to 1-1/2 minutes; remove tea bags and sweeten to taste. Stir in 3 cups ice cubes until melted; keep refrigerated.
Caffeine: 20mg/8 fl oz serving Flavonoids: 80mg/8 fl oz serving
